  "original_title": "\u0dbd\u0dcf\u0dc6\u0dca \u0d9c\u0dd1\u0dc3\u0dca \u0da7\u0ddc\u0db1\u0dca 3,000\u0d9a\u0dca \u0d91\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "3,000 tons of liquefied gas will arrive",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A senior officer of the Laugh Gas Company said that a ship carrying 3,000 metric tons of gas imported by the Laugh Gas Company arrived at the Hambantota port today (16) and the gas stock is to be unloaded at the Laugh Gas Terminal located at the port.",
        "The official said that the production will start after landing the gas and after that the gas cylinders will be released to the market as soon as possible."
      ],
